{"title":"我听到土地的声响","authors":["奥·阿·阿兹哈利"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到土地的声响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔索马里〕奥·阿·阿兹哈利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过诋毁和欺骗的烟幕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到亲爱土地的声响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在索马里的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棕榈在歌唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在索马里的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭壁在鸣响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们啊，振奋着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为和平打仗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的热血胜过中午的太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的无畏精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过狂暴的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从凶手手里夺来刀枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们啊，振奋着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为和平打仗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔黄成浩　译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}